00:46:36,130 --> 00:46:39,640
Because the cause of the claim stated 1 billion won instead of 100 million,

641
00:46:39,640 --> 00:46:42,910
I heard the defendant caused quite an uproar in court.

642
00:46:42,910 --> 00:46:45,650
They broke down in tears, saying it was an amount

643
00:46:45,650 --> 00:46:48,140
